{
  "name": "ColorScale",
  "summary": "<p>所有条件格式对象均包含在 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.FormatConditions\">FormatConditions</a></strong> 集合对象中，该集合对象是 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 集合的子项。您可以使用 <strong>FormatConditions</strong> 集合的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.Add\">Add</a></strong> 或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.AddColorScale\">AddColorScale</a></strong> 方法创建色阶格式规则。</p>\n<p>色阶是直观的参照，可以帮助您了解数据的分布和变化。您可以对数据范围、表中的数据或数据透视表中的数据应用双色或三色色阶。对于双色色阶条件格式，您可以将值、类型和颜色分配给范围的最小和最大阈值。三色色阶还具有中点阈值。</p>\n<p>通过设置 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriteria/ColorScaleCriteria .htm#ColorScaleCriteria.ColorScaleCriteria\">ColorScaleCriteria</a></strong> 对象的属性，可以确定其中的每个阈值。<strong>ColorScaleCriteria</strong> 对象是 <strong>ColorScale</strong> 对象的子项，也是色阶的所有 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriterion/ColorScaleCriterion .htm#ColorScaleCriterion.ColorScaleCriterion\">ColorScaleCriterion</a></strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建了一个数字范围，然后将双色色阶条件格式规则应用于该范围。然后指定最小阈值的颜色为红色，最大阈值的颜色为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Fill cells with sample data from 1 to 10</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFill</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Create a two-color ColorScale object for the created sample data range</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddColorScale</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Set the minimum threshold to red and maximum threshold to blue</span>\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个色阶条件格式所应用于的单元格区域，并设置该条件格式的第一个阈值条件的颜色和亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A7:A8&quot;</span>))\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表色阶条件格式规则。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "AppliesTo",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象，指定格式规则将应用于的单元格区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个色阶条件格式应用到的单元格区域赋值给 C1 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AppliesTo</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中工作表 Sheet1 上区域 A1:A10 中第二个色阶条件格式应用到的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AppliesTo</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorScaleCriteria",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriteria/ColorScaleCriteria .htm#ColorScaleCriteria.ColorScaleCriteria\">ColorScaleCriteria</a></strong> 对象，该对象是单个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriterion/ColorScaleCriterion .htm#ColorScaleCriterion.ColorScaleCriterion\">ColorScaleCriterion</a></strong> 对象的集合。<strong>ColorScaleCriterion</strong> 对象指定用于色阶条件格式的阈值条件的类型、值和颜色。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个色阶条件格式的阈值条件的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个色阶条件格式的第三个阈值条件的类型为xlConditionValueHighestValue，则设置该阈值条件的主题颜色和亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValueHighestValue) {\n        criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent3\n        criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ColorScaleCriteria",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Priority",
      "summary": "<p>设置优先级时，值必须为介于 1 和工作表上条件格式规则总数之间的正整数。对于工作表上的所有规则，优先级必须为唯一值，因此，如果更改指定条件格式规则的优先级，将可能会导致工作表上其他规则的优先级值移位。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置条件格式规则的优先级值。当工作表中存在多个条件格式规则时，优先级确定求值的顺序。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个色阶条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第一个色阶条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "StopIfTrue",
      "summary": "<p>为了支持向后兼容性，此属性的默认值为 <strong>True</strong>，而这与在用户界面中创建的格式规则的行为相反。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，该值确定在当前规则的计算结果为 <strong>True</strong> 时是否应计算单元格上的其他格式规则，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第一个色阶条件格式的计算结果为True时是否停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">StopIfTrue</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;条件格式的计算结果为 True 时停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;条件格式的计算结果为 True 时计算单元格上的其他格式规则&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个色阶条件格式的计算结果为True时是否停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">StopIfTrue</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "<p>此属性将始终返回 <strong>Long</strong> 值“3”，这相当于 <strong>xlColorScale</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlFormatConditionType 枚举.html\">XlFormatConditionType</a></strong> 枚举的常量之一，该常量指定条件格式的类型。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第一个条件格式的类型是否为色阶条件格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlColorScale)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一张工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个条件格式的类型是否为色阶条件格式，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlColorScale) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;类型为色阶条件格式&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;类型不为色阶条件格式&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除指定的条件格式规则对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个色阶条件格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除区域 A1:A10 中第二个色阶条件格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "ModifyAppliesToRange",
      "summary": "<p>该区域必须采用 A1 引用样式，并全部包含在 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.FormatConditions\">FormatConditions</a></strong> 集合的父工作表内。可包括区域操作符（冒号）、相交区域操作符（空格）或合并区域操作符（逗号）。也可以使用货币符号，但会被忽略。</p>\n<p>您也可以在区域的任意部分中使用局部定义名称，但该名称必须使用宏语言。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>设置此格式规则所应用于的单元格区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个色阶条件格式所应用于的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个色阶条件格式所应用于的单元格区域，并设置该条件格式的第一个阈值条件的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A7:A9&quot;</span>))\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Range",
          "type": "Range",
          "description": "<p>此格式规则将应用于的区域。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetFirstPriority",
      "summary": "<p>当工作表中有多个条件格式规则时，如果之前未将此规则设置为优先级“1”，此方法将导致工作表上的所有其他现有规则的优先级都增加 1。</p>\n<p>将在工作表级别应用条件格式规则的优先级。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>将此条件格式规则的优先级值设置为“1”，以便在工作表上的所有其他规则之前计算此规则。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个色阶条件格式的优先级值设置为“1”，并删除该区域上第一个色阶条件格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第二个色阶条件格式的优先级设置为“1”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetLastPriority",
      "summary": "<p>优先级的实际值将等于工作表上条件格式规则的总数。当工作表中有多个条件格式规则时，此方法将导致优先级值大于此规则的规则的优先级降低 1。</p>\n<p>将在工作表级别应用条件格式规则的优先级。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>为此条件格式规则设置求值顺序，以便在工作表上的所有其他规则之后计算此规则。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个色阶条件格式的求值顺序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetLastPriority</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第一个色阶条件格式的求值顺序，并显示该条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetLastPriority</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}